OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan jailed for taking      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbrother's picture in court 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man who took a "light-hearted"       
OL,6, picture of his brother in a court dock 
OL,7, has been jailed for six months.        
OL,9,FLiam Thompson was awaiting the start of
OL,10,Fhis trial on Monday when his brother   
OL,11,FKane took pictures on his phone from a 
OL,12,Fpublic gallery and shared it on social 
OL,13,Fmedia, Newcastle Crown Court heard.    
OL,15,FTaking pictures in court is illegal,   
OL,16,Fwith a judge saying it was "potentially
OL,17,Fdestructive and intimidating conduct". 
OL,19,FKane Thompson, 24, admitted two        
OL,20,Fcontempt of court offences.            
